# Beginner To-Do List ✅

A simple To-Do List web application created using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.  
This project is designed as a beginner-level task to practice DOM manipulation and user interactions.

## 🔧 Features
- Add tasks
- Delete tasks
- Mark tasks as completed
- Save tasks using LocalStorage

## 📂 Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript (Vanilla)

